des:
Flute Meditation Music, a Calming flute track ideal for relaxation and yoga.

If you like to go deeper into meditation, then you should include some lovely and soft music in the background. This will improve your cognitive abilities and help you meditate better. It is also said that those who meditate while listening to music can find inner peace and happiness within themselves.
